# Plan files queued by `sdd approve` are local attestation drafts, not
# committed history. `sdd finalize` materialises them into spec/spec.md
# and moves the plan to .sdd/plans/finalized/. Consumers who want a
# git-audited approval trail can remove this `.gitignore` (see
# CTR-019 / SUR-014 in spec/spec.md for the plan-file format).

*.yaml
.active
finalized/
